		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I believe the voltage would remain the same, but it would draw current from both batteries (and only what it needs).  I <em>think</em> it'd be ok, but don't blame me if something gets fried. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />It's only 2 pins, shouldn't be too hard to remove I'd imagine.  Just add some fresh solder to it if it's not melting properly.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
