		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There are complications.  There are ones that are too tall, but the real issue is the distance between the tabs.  Maybe someone can give a more accurate measurement, but it seems like about 18mm between the tabs.  I haven't found a battery holder that fits right without bending the pins.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
